# Pin all text files to LF line endings.
# Prevents prompt-cache misses caused by Windows checkouts producing CRLF
# while Vercel's Linux build produces LF — the kb-loader now normalizes
# at read time too (defense in depth), but this stops the divergence at
# the working-tree boundary.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Common binary asset types — never touch line endings.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.pdf binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
